      "title": "A weather warning",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology has issued a warning about heavy rains. The Department of Meteorology states that heavy rains of up to 100 mm are expected in some places in Sabaragamuwa, Basnahara and North-West provinces and Galle and Matara districts."
